data.text:
@sjsbates @teachbarefoot Schoolhouse Rock never did a song on Articles, did they?
Verbs, adverbs, nouns, Interjections!
But not articles.

@teachbarefoot Sometimes I forget the term for a, an, and the.... something adjectives.... 

They’re article adjectives. Nobody calls them that. Just “articles.” 

It’s like remembering “Dwayne Johnson” and not “The Rock.”
